I'm pulling you up! 
Hold on to your end!

861
01:29:06,655 --> 01:29:07,704
Go!

862
01:29:07,787 --> 01:29:09,455
No, 
I'm not going anywhere without you!

863
01:29:10,118 --> 01:29:12,787
