02:15:02,976 --> 02:15:04,109
Jack!

1011
02:15:07,199 --> 02:15:08,949
Look after yourself!

1012
02:15:09,599 --> 02:15:11,527
Keep the gate open, will you?

1013
02:15:11,613 --> 02:15:13,272
Sure thing, buddy.

1014
02:15:14,042 --> 02:15:15,371
Good luck!

1015
02:15:28,627 --> 02:15:30,009
I'm sorry.

