02:18:08,836 --> 02:18:09,920
Ann.

1017
02:19:18,442 --> 02:19:19,527
Jack!

1018
02:19:20,404 --> 02:19:21,527
Run!

1019
02:19:51,798 --> 02:19:53,423
Jack, Jack!

1020
02:20:01,140 --> 02:20:02,299
Jack.

