Not yet.

1032
02:22:24,009 --> 02:22:25,126
Wait.

1033
02:22:25,798 --> 02:22:26,891
Wait.

1034
02:22:31,009 --> 02:22:32,140
Wait!

1035
02:22:42,855 --> 02:22:44,065
Come on!

